<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmaccāḷukyavikramavarṣada 49neya krōdhisaṁvatsa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rada vaiśākhabakuḷa cauti Ādivārada<unclear>ṁ</unclear>ddu śrīmattribhu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vanamalladēvara magaḷu jayakēsidēva na<unclear>rdhāṁ</unclear>galakṣmi maiḷala
<lb n="4" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> sida
</p>

